sentences.sContent: Meat from New Zealand is frozen and brought to England in special ships.
sentences.sCn: 从新西兰运来的肉被冷冻保藏，用特殊的船运往英国。

sentences.sContent: If you live in Australia, the US, the UK, Canada or New Zealand, then you live in the same place as me; Fat City.
sentences.sCn: 如果你是生活在澳大利亚，美国，加拿大或者新西兰，那么你其实就是和我住在同一个地方：肥胖国。

sentences.sContent: Unfortunately, we know that one effect of climate change in New Zealand will be more extreme weather like this.
sentences.sCn: 遗憾的是，我们知道，气候变化在新西兰的影响之一是会有更多像这样的极端天气。
